#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.29"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.29:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.29:0.2"
msgid "3. Koṭigāmavagga"
msgstr "3. At the Village of Koṭi"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.29:0.3"
msgid "29. Pariññeyyasutta"
msgstr "29. Should Be Completely Understood"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.436"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.29:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, ariyasaccāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four noble truths."

msgctxt "sn56.29:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn56.29:1.3"
msgid ""
"Dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhaṃ "
"ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"The noble truths of suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of "
"suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering."

msgctxt "sn56.29:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri ariyasaccāni."
msgstr "These are the four noble truths."

msgctxt "sn56.29:1.5"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ atthi ariyasaccaṃ pariññeyyaṃ, "
"atthi ariyasaccaṃ pahātabbaṃ, atthi ariyasaccaṃ sacchikātabbaṃ, atthi "
"ariyasaccaṃ bhāvetabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Of these four noble truths, there is one to be completely understood, one to "
"be given up, one to be realized, and one to be developed."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.29:2.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, ariyasaccaṃ pariññeyyaṃ?"
msgstr "And which noble truth should be completely understood?"

msgctxt "sn56.29:2.2"
msgid ""
"Dukkhaṃ, bhikkhave, ariyasaccaṃ pariññeyyaṃ, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ "
"pahātabbaṃ, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ sacchikātabbaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminī "
"paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ bhāvetabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The noble truth of suffering should be completely understood. The noble "
"truth of the origin of suffering should be given up. The noble truth of the "
"cessation of suffering should be realized. The noble truth of the practice "
"that leads to the cessation of suffering should be developed."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.29:3.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.29:3.2"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
